  "title": "fix(instantsearch): warn deprecated usage of `searchParameters`",
  "body": "> This PR targets the `develop` branch, thus InstantSearch.js 3.\r\n\r\nThis displays a development warning when using `searchParameters` on InstantSearch.js 3. This option doesn't exist anymore on v4 and therefore it's better to warn users before reading the migration guide. We instead advise for using the `configure` widget.",
